{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|2Ti|1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","chapter":1,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":1,"verse":1,"text":"Paul, an apostle of Christ Jesus by God’s will, for the sake of the promise of life in Christ Jesus:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":1,"verse":2,"text":"To Timothy, my dearly loved son. Grace, mercy, and peace from God the Father and Christ Jesus our Lord.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":1,"verse":3,"text":"I thank God, whom I serve with a clear conscience as my ancestors did, when I constantly remember you in my prayers night and day.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":1,"verse":4,"text":"Remembering your tears, I long to see you so that I may be filled with joy.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":1,"verse":5,"text":"I recall your sincere faith that first lived in your grandmother Lois and in your mother Eunice and now, I am convinced, is in you also.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":1,"verse":6,"text":"Therefore, I remind you to rekindle the gift of God that is in you through the laying on of my hands.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":1,"verse":7,"text":"For God has not given us a spirit of fear, but one of power, love, and sound judgment.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":1,"verse":8,"text":"So don’t be ashamed of the testimony about our Lord, or of me his prisoner. Instead, share in suffering for the gospel, relying on the power of God.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":1,"verse":9,"text":"He has saved us and called us with a holy calling, not according to our works, but according to his own purpose and grace, which was given to us in Christ Jesus before time began.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":1,"verse":10,"text":"This has now been made evident through the appearing of our Savior Christ Jesus, who has abolished death and has brought life and immortality to light through the gospel.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":1,"verse":11,"text":"For this gospel I was appointed a herald, apostle, and teacher,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":1,"verse":12,"text":"and that is why I suffer these things. But I am not ashamed, because I know whom I have believed and am persuaded that he is able to guard what has been entrusted to me until that day.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":1,"verse":13,"text":"Hold on to the pattern of sound teaching that you have heard from me, in the faith and love that are in Christ Jesus.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":1,"verse":14,"text":"Guard the good deposit through the Holy Spirit who lives in us.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":1,"verse":15,"text":"You know that all those in the province of Asia have deserted me, including Phygelus and Hermogenes.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":1,"verse":16,"text":"May the Lord grant mercy to the household of Onesiphorus, because he often refreshed me and was not ashamed of my chains.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":1,"verse":17,"text":"On the contrary, when he was in Rome, he diligently searched for me and found me.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","bookOrder":54,"chapter":1,"verse":18,"text":"May the Lord grant that he obtain mercy from him on that day. You know very well how much he ministered at Ephesus.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"2Ti","chapter":1,"paragraphStarts":[1,2,3,6,8,13],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"Greeting"},{"beforeVerse":3,"text":"Thanksgiving"},{"beforeVerse":8,"text":"Not Ashamed of the Gospel"},{"beforeVerse":13,"text":"Be Loyal to the Faith"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Paul, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:9","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" an apostle of Christ Jesus by God’s will, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 1:1","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 1:1","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 1:1","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" for the sake of the promise of life "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 2:25","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":25,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 5:12","book":"1Jn","chapter":5,"verse":12,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" in Christ Jesus:"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 13:9","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":9},{"label":"1Co 1:1","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":1},{"label":"Eph 1:1","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":1},{"label":"Col 1:1","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":1},{"label":"1Jn 2:25","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":25},{"label":"1Jn 5:12","book":"1Jn","chapter":5,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"To Timothy, my dearly loved son."},{"kind":"text","text":" Grace, mercy, and peace "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 1:2","book":"1Ti","chapter":1,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Jn 3","book":"2Jn","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" from God the Father and Christ Jesus our Lord."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Tm 1:2","book":"1Ti","chapter":1,"verse":2},{"label":"2Jn 3","book":"2Jn","chapter":1,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I thank God, whom I serve with a clear conscience "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 23:1","book":"Act","chapter":23,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 24:16","book":"Act","chapter":24,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 9:1","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 1:12","book":"2Co","chapter":1,"verse":12,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 1:19","book":"1Ti","chapter":1,"verse":19,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 3:9","book":"1Ti","chapter":3,"verse":9,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 10:22","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":22,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 3:21","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":21,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" as my ancestors did, when I constantly remember you in my prayers night and day. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 1:6","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":6,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 23:1","book":"Act","chapter":23,"verse":1},{"label":"Ac 24:16","book":"Act","chapter":24,"verse":16},{"label":"Rm 9:1","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":1},{"label":"2Co 1:12","book":"2Co","chapter":1,"verse":12},{"label":"1Tm 1:19","book":"1Ti","chapter":1,"verse":19},{"label":"1Tm 3:9","book":"1Ti","chapter":3,"verse":9},{"label":"Heb 10:22","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":22},{"label":"1Pt 3:21","book":"1Pe","chapter":3,"verse":21},{"label":"Eph 1:6","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Remembering your tears, I long to see you so that I may be filled with joy. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I recall your sincere faith "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 1:5","book":"1Ti","chapter":1,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" that first lived in your grandmother Lois and in your mother Eunice "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 16:1","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and now, I am convinced, is in you also."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Tm 1:5","book":"1Ti","chapter":1,"verse":5},{"label":"Ac 16:1","book":"Act","chapter":16,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore, I remind you to rekindle the gift of God that is in you through the laying on of my hands. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 4:14","book":"1Ti","chapter":4,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 5:22","book":"1Ti","chapter":5,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Tm 4:14","book":"1Ti","chapter":4,"verse":14},{"label":"1Tm 5:22","book":"1Ti","chapter":5,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For God has not given us a spirit of fear, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 7:13","book":"Jhn","chapter":7,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 14:27","book":"Jhn","chapter":14,"verse":27,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:15","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":15,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" but one of power, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or For the Spirit God gave us does not make us fearful, but gives us power"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 1:35","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":35,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 4:14","book":"Luk","chapter":4,"verse":14,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 24:49","book":"Luk","chapter":24,"verse":49,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 1:8","book":"Act","chapter":1,"verse":8,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 4:33","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":33,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 15:13","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":13,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 15:19","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":19,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 2:4","book":"1Co","chapter":2,"verse":4,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 3:16","book":"Eph","chapter":3,"verse":16,"letter":"l"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 3:20","book":"Eph","chapter":3,"verse":20,"letter":"m"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 1:5","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":5,"letter":"n"},{"kind":"text","text":" love, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 13:1","book":"1Co","chapter":13,"verse":1,"letter":"o"},{"kind":"text","text":" and sound judgment."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 7:13","book":"Jhn","chapter":7,"verse":13},{"label":"Jn 14:27","book":"Jhn","chapter":14,"verse":27},{"label":"Rm 8:15","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":15},{"label":"Lk 1:35","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":35},{"label":"Lk 4:14","book":"Luk","chapter":4,"verse":14},{"label":"Lk 24:49","book":"Luk","chapter":24,"verse":49},{"label":"Ac 1:8","book":"Act","chapter":1,"verse":8},{"label":"Ac 4:33","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":33},{"label":"Rm 15:13","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":13},{"label":"Rm 15:19","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":19},{"label":"1Co 2:4","book":"1Co","chapter":2,"verse":4},{"label":"Eph 3:16","book":"Eph","chapter":3,"verse":16},{"label":"Eph 3:20","book":"Eph","chapter":3,"verse":20},{"label":"1Th 1:5","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":5},{"label":"1Co 13:1","book":"1Co","chapter":13,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or For the Spirit God gave us does not make us fearful, but gives us power"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So don’t be ashamed "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 8:38","book":"Mrk","chapter":8,"verse":38,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:16","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 1:12","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":12,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 1:16","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":16,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" of the testimony about our Lord, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 4:33","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":33,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 1:6","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":6,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 1:2","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":2,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 1:9","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":9,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 12:17","book":"Rev","chapter":12,"verse":17,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 19:10","book":"Rev","chapter":19,"verse":10,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 20:4","book":"Rev","chapter":20,"verse":4,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"text","text":" or of me his prisoner. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 3:1","book":"Eph","chapter":3,"verse":1,"letter":"l"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 4:1","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":1,"letter":"m"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Phm 1","book":"Phm","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"n"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Phm 1:9","book":"Phm","chapter":1,"verse":9,"letter":"o"},{"kind":"text","text":" Instead, share in suffering for the gospel, relying on the power "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 1:35","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":35,"letter":"p"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 13:4","book":"2Co","chapter":13,"verse":4,"letter":"q"},{"kind":"text","text":" of God. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 8:38","book":"Mrk","chapter":8,"verse":38},{"label":"Rm 1:16","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":16},{"label":"2Tm 1:12","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":12},{"label":"2Tm 1:16","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":16},{"label":"Ac 4:33","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":33},{"label":"1Co 1:6","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":6},{"label":"Rv 1:2","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":2},{"label":"Rv 1:9","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":9},{"label":"Rv 12:17","book":"Rev","chapter":12,"verse":17},{"label":"Rv 19:10","book":"Rev","chapter":19,"verse":10},{"label":"Rv 20:4","book":"Rev","chapter":20,"verse":4},{"label":"Eph 3:1","book":"Eph","chapter":3,"verse":1},{"label":"Eph 4:1","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":1},{"label":"Phm 1","book":"Phm","chapter":1,"verse":1},{"label":"Phm 1:9","book":"Phm","chapter":1,"verse":9},{"label":"Lk 1:35","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":35},{"label":"2Co 13:4","book":"2Co","chapter":13,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:2Ti:1:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He has saved us and called us with a holy calling, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:28","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":28,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 11:14","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 11:29","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":29,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 3:1","book":"Heb","chapter":3,"verse":1,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" not according to our works, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 2:9","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":9,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" but according to his own purpose "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 19:21","book":"Pro","chapter":19,"verse":21,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 42:6","book":"Isa","chapter":42,"verse":6,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 46:10","book":"Isa","chapter":46,"verse":10,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 2:23","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":23,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 4:28","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":28,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 26:16","book":"Act","chapter":26,"verse":16,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:28","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":28,"letter":"l"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 9:11","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":11,"letter":"m"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 1:11","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":11,"letter":"n"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 2:13","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":13,"letter":"o"},{"kind":"text","text":" and grace, which was given to us in Christ Jesus before time began. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 8:28","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":28},{"label":"Rm 11:14","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":14},{"label":"Rm 11:29","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":29},{"label":"Heb 3:1","book":"Heb","chapter":3,"verse":1},{"label":"Eph 2:9","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":9},{"label":"Pr 19:21","book":"Pro","chapter":19,"verse":21},{"label":"Is 42:6","book":"Isa","chapter":42,"verse":6},{"label":"Is 46:10","book":"Isa","chapter":46,"verse":10},{"label":"Ac 2:23","book":"Act","chapter":2,"verse":23},{"label":"Ac 4:28","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":28},{"label":"Ac 26:16","book":"Act","chapter":26,"verse":16